name: Reegesk (V)
Lore: 'Ranat thief and scavenger from Aralia. Regularly trades with Jawas. Adept at pilfering items without alerting the owner. Willing to steal anything, even trash.',
Text: 'During opponent''s turn, if present at a battleground site, may steal a device, droid, starfighter, vehicle, or weapon in opponent''s Lost Pile into your hand.',
